# Same Schwarzschild metric as schwarzschild_ascii.od, LaTeX-flavored
# spelling of the same SCALAR_EXPR grammar -- must produce identical
# results (DESIGN-UI.md 6.1: one grammar, two token spellings).
manifold M dim 4
bundle TM on M dim 4
chart schw on M coords (t, r, theta, phi)
metric g on schw bundle TM {
  g_{tt} = -\left(1 - \frac{2M}{r}\right),
  g_{rr} = \frac{1}{1 - \frac{2M}{r}},
  g_{\theta\theta} = r^2,
  g_{\phi\phi} = r^2 \sin^2(\theta)
}
